From: Abderrahim Kitouni <akitouni@gnome.org>
Date: Sat, 7 Mar 2026 16:08:48 +0100
Subject: [PATCH] Update elements/include/linux.yml to v6.19.6-0

Updates elements/include/linux.yml to v6.19.6-0 (6a75390)
Previous version was v6.18.9-0 (adb851e)

This also removes CRYPTO_ANSI_CPRNG, dropped upstream
---
 elements/include/linux.yml  | 2 +-
 files/linux/fdsdk-config.sh | 1 -
 2 files changed, 1 insertion(+), 2 deletions(-)

diff --git a/elements/include/linux.yml b/elements/include/linux.yml
index 29c1f74c2..cd09493d1 100644
--- a/elements/include/linux.yml
+++ b/elements/include/linux.yml
@@ -4,6 +4,6 @@ sources:
   track: v*
   exclude:
   - '*-rc*'
-  ref: v6.18.7-0-g5dfbc5357c34bdf81c84aa78bc8e3d6d9ba10aad
+  ref: v6.19.6-0-g6a753907865e35ae986b7b2ad48daa1eab4bcf3a
 - kind: patch_queue
   path: patches/linux
diff --git a/files/linux/fdsdk-config.sh b/files/linux/fdsdk-config.sh
index 120d88938..bd4395419 100644
--- a/files/linux/fdsdk-config.sh
+++ b/files/linux/fdsdk-config.sh
@@ -89,7 +89,6 @@ module CRYPTO_ADIANTUM
 module CRYPTO_AEGIS128
 module CRYPTO_AES
 module CRYPTO_AES_TI
-module CRYPTO_ANSI_CPRNG
 module CRYPTO_ARC4
 module CRYPTO_BLOWFISH
 module CRYPTO_CAMELLIA
